Welcome to the Garden Planner App for Android.  This app is available through download in the Google Play Store.

This app was originally created as a school project.  As the app is a very simple format, all data used on the app is stored on your own device.

No data from your installation of the app is shared or accessible to anyone else.

If you wish to remove app data from your phone, simply clear all fields from the app, or delete the app entirely from your phone.

If you have any questions or concerns about the app or any bug fix or security concerns, please reach out:

